a:50:{i:1317919;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1317919";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"1";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"44";s:6:"handle";s:9:"Marceline";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"950";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";s:13:"Rabble_Rouser";s:4:"text";s:8:"Sowwy :c";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1428363868";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#e79c3e";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14283638683";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#d82520";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1317920;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1317920";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"1";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"37";s:6:"handle";s:13:"Rabble_Rouser";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"757";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";s:9:"Marceline";s:4:"text";s:56:"What&#039;s gonna happen to her if Unrest gets replaced?";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1428363906";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#c8b562";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14283639056";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#0f6e4e";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1317921;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1317921";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"1";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"44";s:6:"handle";s:9:"Marceline";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"950";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";s:13:"Rabble_Rouser";s:4:"text";s:14:"... I dunno :c";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1428363919";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#e79c3e";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14283639210";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#d82520";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1318165;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1318165";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"1";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"37";s:6:"handle";s:13:"Rabble_Rouser";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"757";s:17:"recipient_user_id";s:2:"15";s:18:"recipient_username";s:7:"Regulus";s:4:"text";s:97:"If Tek hasn&#039;t told you, I&#039;ve been playing around with making a replacement for Unrest. ";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1428368224";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#c8b562";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14283682239";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#0f6e4e";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1318171;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1318171";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"1";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"15";s:6:"handle";s:7:"Regulus";s:12:"character_id";s:2:"49";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";s:13:"Rabble_Rouser";s:4:"text";s:13:"No he has not";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1428368262";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#3eb820";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14283682556";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#7eee5b";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1318227;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1318227";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"1";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"37";s:6:"handle";s:13:"Rabble_Rouser";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"757";s:17:"recipient_user_id";s:2:"15";s:18:"recipient_username";s:7:"Regulus";s:4:"text";s:1467:"Well, it&#039;s in a simple form now, just a basic setting. The idea of having a setting like that is to create a place where high adventures could exist while still being very much pony fitting. We&#039;ve seen in the show that they have their own fictional settings from their books/comics and the like. Well, the plan was to have a setting where all those fictional universes inside the show would bleed together, creating an anaglam world for the characters. For simplicity, I&#039;d compare it to League of Extraordinary Gentleman, the Fable&#039;s series, or DC Comic&#039;s Infinite Crisis. The characters are all being entered into this world by a process called &#039;The Bleed&#039; where, as imagined, their universes bleed into one with the other ones. This would allow for the big events that were promised with Unrest, yet be able to restrict things for a person&#039;s personal event. Though the world would be an anaglam, parts of it would favor genres, to give a distinct theme to that place in the world. There&#039;d be old style victorian townships for the most trying of Van Helsing / Lovecraftian horror and suspense, a prospering metropolis for super powered shenanigans, a great sea for the golden age of saltiness, and a stalwart castle for knightly heroics. &#039;The Bleed&#039; would also account for keeping these characters it equal with each others universes, as if you stray too far from your own settings, your character would adapt. ";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1428369190";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#c8b562";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14283691903";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#0f6e4e";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1318232;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1318232";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"1";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"15";s:6:"handle";s:7:"Regulus";s:12:"character_id";s:2:"49";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";s:13:"Rabble_Rouser";s:4:"text";s:74:"I assume your going to put this all together for a big pitch to the staff?";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1428369243";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#3eb820";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14283692447";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#7eee5b";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1318234;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1318234";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"1";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"15";s:6:"handle";s:7:"Regulus";s:12:"character_id";s:2:"49";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";s:13:"Rabble_Rouser";s:4:"text";s:36:"And yes I am reading this as I typed";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1428369254";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#3eb820";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14283692540";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#7eee5b";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1318237;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1318237";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"1";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"37";s:6:"handle";s:13:"Rabble_Rouser";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"757";s:17:"recipient_user_id";s:2:"15";s:18:"recipient_username";s:7:"Regulus";s:4:"text";s:56:"Yes, once I get it to a level I&#039;m comfortable with.";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1428369301";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#c8b562";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14283693015";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#0f6e4e";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1318238;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1318238";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"1";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"15";s:6:"handle";s:7:"Regulus";s:12:"character_id";s:2:"49";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";s:13:"Rabble_Rouser";s:4:"text";s:157:"Btw if you are looking for a way to have all these worlds &quot;bleed&quot; together I have two possible ways to help you. Both from the comics and the show.";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1428369301";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#3eb820";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14283693032";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#7eee5b";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1318239;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1318239";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"1";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"37";s:6:"handle";s:13:"Rabble_Rouser";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"757";s:17:"recipient_user_id";s:2:"15";s:18:"recipient_username";s:7:"Regulus";s:4:"text";s:88:"I&#039;m always open to ideas. A good world is not built on the shoulders of one alone. ";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1428369355";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#c8b562";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14283693551";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#0f6e4e";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1318248;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1318248";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"1";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"15";s:6:"handle";s:7:"Regulus";s:12:"character_id";s:2:"49";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";s:13:"Rabble_Rouser";s:4:"text";s:52:"http://mlp.wikia.com/wiki/IDW_comics_sixth_story_arc";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1428369413";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#3eb820";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14283694149";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#7eee5b";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1318252;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1318252";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"1";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"15";s:6:"handle";s:7:"Regulus";s:12:"character_id";s:2:"49";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";s:13:"Rabble_Rouser";s:4:"text";s:88:"The book worms apparently have an ability to take the written word and make them appear.";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1428369453";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#3eb820";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14283694549";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#7eee5b";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1318256;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1318256";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"1";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"15";s:6:"handle";s:7:"Regulus";s:12:"character_id";s:2:"49";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";s:13:"Rabble_Rouser";s:4:"text";s:161:"Imagine [i]if[/i] there was a group of book worms that collected various stories, comics, books, etc and connected them into a big web to form a library of sorts";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1428369488";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#3eb820";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14283694894";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#7eee5b";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1318260;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1318260";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"1";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"15";s:6:"handle";s:7:"Regulus";s:12:"character_id";s:2:"49";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";s:13:"Rabble_Rouser";s:4:"text";s:75:"That library charged with their magic results in this patched worked world.";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1428369540";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#3eb820";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14283695418";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#7eee5b";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1318261;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1318261";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"1";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"37";s:6:"handle";s:13:"Rabble_Rouser";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"757";s:17:"recipient_user_id";s:2:"15";s:18:"recipient_username";s:7:"Regulus";s:4:"text";s:211:"It would be of similar effect, but I was thinking of romanticising it to seem more appealing, the first idea was to make it Starswirl the Bearded&#039;s library. Though I&#039;m not exactly keen on keeping that.";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1428369565";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#c8b562";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14283695654";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#0f6e4e";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1318263;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1318263";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"1";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"15";s:6:"handle";s:7:"Regulus";s:12:"character_id";s:2:"49";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";s:13:"Rabble_Rouser";s:4:"text";s:134:"I wouldn&#039;t be keen on that too. The comics had provided some great insight on Starswirl that I highly recommend others to look up";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1428369600";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#3eb820";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14283696009";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#7eee5b";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1318265;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1318265";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"1";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"15";s:6:"handle";s:7:"Regulus";s:12:"character_id";s:2:"49";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";s:13:"Rabble_Rouser";s:4:"text";s:181:"I would say [i]however[/i] another way to go about this is the mirror portals and having an &quot;axis&quot; point where bits and pieces of the various universes are reflected there";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1428369636";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#3eb820";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14283696374";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#7eee5b";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1318292;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1318292";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"1";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"37";s:6:"handle";s:13:"Rabble_Rouser";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"757";s:17:"recipient_user_id";s:2:"15";s:18:"recipient_username";s:7:"Regulus";s:4:"text";s:974:"Well, I do keep the fact the comic and show are separate universes themselves. Otherwise though, the idea has had no dislikes as of yet, and it certainly fits all the spots the site wanted from a high adventure universe. The problem would be managment. There&#039;d have to be specific content supervisors for just that world alone. Those who could help keep players from being overpowered and on level with each other. &#039;Librarians&#039; for the sake of kinship to the setting. They&#039;d be the ones approving characters and ideas for events, yet still fall under the rules of the site and moderation by the Guides. Sapphire would be my first choice of a Guide to overview it all. She has the most experience of the guide team out of making non-pony things pony. Librarians would only exist for content approval for the universe, and help keep things equal by assisting with the Bleed and it&#039;s changes on each thing that does appear or decide to cross settings. ";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1428370182";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#c8b562";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14283701824";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#0f6e4e";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1318311;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1318311";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"1";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"15";s:6:"handle";s:7:"Regulus";s:12:"character_id";s:2:"49";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";s:13:"Rabble_Rouser";s:4:"text";s:60:"I&#039;ve been incorporating ideas of the comics to the site";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1428370489";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#3eb820";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14283704901";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#7eee5b";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1318313;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1318313";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"1";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"15";s:6:"handle";s:7:"Regulus";s:12:"character_id";s:2:"49";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";s:13:"Rabble_Rouser";s:4:"text";s:93:"And in fact I&#039;m currently engaging in making an offical list of what has been introduced";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1428370501";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#3eb820";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14283705028";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#7eee5b";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1318328;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1318328";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"1";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"37";s:6:"handle";s:13:"Rabble_Rouser";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"757";s:17:"recipient_user_id";s:2:"15";s:18:"recipient_username";s:7:"Regulus";s:4:"text";s:153:"Nice. I still want the universe to be a bit further detracted from that, just to make sure no players think they can affect one universe with the other. ";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1428370645";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#c8b562";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14283706425";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#0f6e4e";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"view